        "text": "A bold, heavy solid black icon of a thick, pocket-sized spiral-bound notebook. Front 3/4 view. One single, substantial contiguous dark mass of the cover and the spiral binding. High-contrast woodblock style. The left vertical edge is defined by a rhythmic, repeating pattern of four or five chunky, horizontal white negative space 'slashes' to represent the spiral wire. These are thick, geometric voids, not fine lines. A single, massive diagonal white negative space 'slash' is carved into the bottom-right corner of the black mass to represent a 'dog-eared' or folded page corner. No lines on the page, no text, heavy visual weight. Isolated on white. Optimized for a clean, single-boolean SVG silhouette.",
